class="entry-content-section"><h3 id="the-indigenous-marketing-company" class="entry-website-title">The Indigenous Marketing Company</h3><div
class="entry-website-img"><div
class="entry-faux-browser"><div
class="entry-browser-menu"><div
class="dot"></div><div
class="dot"></div><div
class="dot"></div></div>
<picture>
<source
data-srcset="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-the-indigenous-marketing-company-3840x12772-20240613.webp?crop=2:1,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=332&dpr=2" media="(max-width: 412px)" />
<source
data-srcset="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-the-indigenous-marketing-company-3840x12772-20240613.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=495&dpr=2" media="(max-width: 575px)" />
<img
class="lazyload"
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-the-indigenous-marketing-company-3840x12772-20240613.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=650&dpr=2"
width="650"
height="403"
alt="desktop screenshot of website The Indigenous Marketing Company"
/>
</picture></div></div><p
class="entry-website-detail website-detail-url">
<span
class="icon">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-link.svg" alt="chain icon" width="29" height="29" />
</span>
<a
class="force-single-line" href="https://imcmarketing.ca/" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">
https://imcmarketing.ca/
</a></p><p
class="entry-website-detail website-detail-location">
<span
class="icon">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-pin.svg" alt="pin icon" width="30" height="30" />
</span>
<span>Headingley, Manitoba, Canada</span></p><div
class="entry-text"><p>The Indigenous Marketing Company is an Indigenous-owned business that specializes in WordPress web design, SEO, and PPC advertising services. The website's visually-impactful hero image of a fire, accompanied by the tagline "Ignite your potential," is a clever and engaging way to effectively convey the company's ethos.</p><p>The company's Indigenous ownership adds diversity and cultural relevance to their services, while their credentials as a Certified Aboriginal Business (CCAB) reinforce their commitment to Indigenous communities.</p></div><h4>Pros and Cons</h4><div
class="entry-indented-box"><div
class="entry-website-pros">
<span
class="icon icon-sm">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-plus.svg" alt="plus sign" width="18" height="18" />
</span><div
